race.description: Ladbrokes Mates Mode Pots Max 150 Points
race.comment: SHE'S SAVVY (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 22.57 beating Little Bit Super. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Form reads well for this. MAGIC FLETCH (3) is worth forgiving last start after finishing seventh (22.93) in a Grade 5 at this track over 400m. Bold showing expected. JILLIBY DYMAR (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at Richmond Straight. Has the ability and expected to do much better. ALFIE'S PRINCESS (7) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.
